[src:progressive-web-apps/progressive-web-apps] Developers can use web app manifest members to describe a PWA, customize its appearance, and more deeply integrate it into the operating system.
[src:progressive-web-apps/progressive-web-apps] Allows a service worker to send a message to its client PWA.
[src:progressive-web-apps/progressive-web-apps] Allows a service worker and its client PWA to establish a basic two-way communication channel.
